text: Francis Van den Eynde (1 April 1946 â€“ 4 March 2021) was a Belgian politician. He was a member of the Flemish Movement and was part of the Vlaams Blok and Vlaams Belang. He was a member of the Chamber of Representatives from 1991 to 2010. He was born in Brussels, Belgium. Eynde died on 4 March 2021 in Aalst, Belgium at the age of 74. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Politicians from Brussels Category:Flemish politicians
